topic: Sport Workflow Series ("FIFA World Cup events explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for connecting national football teams with the participations in the finals or in the world cups
goals.2: Identify the BGP that connects a country with a national footbal team or as a location to a world cup
goals.3: In which countries took place a FIFA world cup or world cup final? With how many participants?
goals.4: Compare number of participants and winners of different world cups
goals.4.1: How many times each country participated in a world cup?
goals.4.2: Which country participated in the most finals? Which country won the most finals?
goals.4.3: Who participated in the most world cups among Italy, France, Spain, and Germany?

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pname (COUNT(?p) AS ?number) WHERE { ?team wdt:P31 wd:Q6979593; ?p ?obj. ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pname . } GROUP BY ?p ?pname ORDER BY DESC (?number)
output: category for members of a team
on focus list of Wikimedia project
